components.name: Validate Color Parameter
components.description: Validates the 'color' DAG parameter to ensure correct environment targeting before pipeline execution.

upstream_policy.description: First task in the linear pipeline.

components.name: Download Mondo OBO File
components.description: Downloads the latest Mondo OBO file from GitHub releases, checks version against S3, and uploads the file to S3, skipping if uptodate.

components.name: Normalize Mondo Terms
components.description: Processes the downloaded Mondo OBO file with Spark to normalize ontology terms, excluding specific identifiers, and writes results to the public Mondo terms location in S3.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the OBO file has been successfully downloaded to S3.

connections.purpose: Read OBO file and write normalized terms

components.name: Index Mondo Terms
components.description: Loads the normalized Mondo terms into Elasticsearch using a Spark job with a predefined index mapping template.
outputs: Elasticsearch index containing Mondo ontology data

upstream_policy.description: Runs after normalized terms have been written to S3.

components.name: Publish Mondo Dataset
components.description: Publishes the indexed Mondo data to downstream systems, using the version from the download step and the environment color parameter.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the Elasticsearch indexing step completes successfully.

components.name: Send Slack Notification
components.description: Sends a Slack message via webhook when the pipeline completes successfully.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the Mondo dataset has been published without errors.
